---
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import HandshakeIMG from "../assets/images/business-deal-2.jpeg";
import WebDevIMG from "../assets/images/web-dev-2.jpeg";
---

<!-- SBS -->
<section id="sbs-97">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <!-- Left Image Section -->
        <picture class="cs-picture">
            <source
                media="(max-width: 600px)"
                srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/SideBySide/medical-m.jpg"
            />
            <source
                media="(min-width: 601px)"
                srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/SideBySide/medical.jpg"
            />
            <img
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                src="https://csimg.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/SideBySide/medical.jpg"
                alt="body builder"
                width="500"
                height="552"
                aria-hidden="true"
            />
        </picture>
        <!-- Right Content Section-->
        <div class="cs-content">
            <span class="cs-topper">About Us</span>
            <h2 class="cs-title">Where Problem Solving Meets Design</h2>
            <p class="cs-text">
                My name is Eddie, founder and lead developer of Bay Breeze Web
                Studio. I have always loved building, both physical and digital,
                which led to an early interest in web development.
                <br /><br />
                The journey began when I was about 14, more than a decade ago, after
                a friend showed me his work as a head front-end developer. His mentorship
                gave me a strong starting point, and I credit much of my early progress
                to what he shared. Each new concept, from syntax to patterns and
                problem-solving, revealed how precisely we can direct a computer.
                <br /><br />
                After high school, life took a different route. HVAC work and marriage
                came first. HVAC sharpened problem-solving and systems thinking,
                lessons that still guide how projects are planned and executed. When
                I returned to code and began building sites for friends and family,
                it became clear that many businesses still lacked reliable, performance-focused
                options in a digital-first market.
                <br /><br />
                New AI website builders continued to promise easy solutions. The
                tradeoff was familiar. Performance, user experience, and accessibility
                were too often sacrificed for surface-level convenience, which slowed
                sites, weakened usability, and increased accessibility compliance
                risk.
                <br /><br />
                That is why I founded Bay Breeze Web Studio. The goal is to deliver
                fast, accessible, conversion-focused websites that help businesses
                compete with confidence.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- SBS Reverse -->

<section id="sbsr-2202">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-content">
            <h2 class="cs-title">Time for a Change</h2>
            <p class="cs-text">
                I set out to build websites the right way: accessible to anyone,
                anywhere, powered by clean, custom code for speed and
                reliability. Research quickly revealed a problem in the market,
                agencies charging thousands upfront for static sites clients
                could not update, then billing premium fees for the smallest
                edits. The answer was to remove the barrier and put control back
                in the hands of business owners. Premium websites for everyone,
                with a clear model: <strong
                    >$0 upfront and $149 per month</strong
                >.
                <br /><br />
                From those first builds for friends and family to new client launches,
                the results have been consistent: faster load times, stronger accessibility,
                cleaner user journeys, and better conversions. The process stays
                disciplined, performance first, usability second, maintainability
                always, so sites are built to last and easy to evolve.
                <br /><br />
                The excitement that started at fourteen is still here. Every new
                project brings the same focus and energy, a reminder that this work
                matters because it helps real businesses show up stronger and compete
                with confidence.
                <br /><br />
                Iâ€™m ready to partner with you next and build something fast, accessible,
                and high-converting for your business.
            </p>

            <a href="/contact" class="cs-button-solid">Get Your Website Today</a
            >
        </div>
        <div class="cs-image-group">
            <!--Main Image-->
            <picture class="cs-picture cs-picture1">
                <Image
                    src={HandshakeIMG}
                    alt=""
                    format="webp"
                    height={1250}
                    width={1000}
                    quality={"high"}
                />
            </picture>
            <!--Small Image-->
            <picture class="cs-picture cs-picture2">
                <Image
                    src={WebDevIMG}
                    alt=""
                    format="webp"
                    height={1250}
                    width={1000}
                    quality={"high"}
                />
            </picture>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<CTA />

<!-- Second Style -->
<style>
    /*-- -------------------------- -->
    <---       Side By Side 1       -->
    <--- -------------------------- -*/

    /* Mobile - 360px */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
        #sbs-97 {
            padding: var(--sectionPadding);
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-container {
            width: 100%;
            /* changes to 1280px at tablet */
            max-width: 34.375rem;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            /* 48px - 64px, changed clamp at tablet */
            gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-content {
            /* set text align to left if content needs to be left aligned */
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 33.875rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            /* centers content horizontally, set to flex-start to left align */
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        #sbs-97 .cs-title {
            max-width: 17ch;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-text {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-text:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-ul {
            margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
            /* 16px - 20px */
            padding-left: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-li {
            list-style: none;
            /* 14px - 18px */
            font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.3vw, 1.125rem);
            line-height: 1.5em;
            /* 8px - 12px */
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 1vw, 0.75rem);
            color: var(--bodyTextColor);
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-li:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-number {
            /* 14px - 16px */
            font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.6vw, 1rem);
            /* 24px - 28px */
            width: clamp(1.5rem, 2.9vw, 1.75rem);
            height: clamp(1.5rem, 2.9vw, 1.75rem);
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            /* we set this element to align to the top of the li, so if there's 
                multiple lines it will stay at the top instead of the center of the text */
            align-self: flex-start;
            /* prevents flexbox from squishing it */
            flex: none;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-button-solid {
            font-size: 1rem;
            /* 46px - 56px */
            line-height: clamp(2.875rem, 5.5vw, 3.5rem);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
            min-width: 9.375rem;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            /* prevents padding from adding to the width */
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-button-solid:before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            background: #000;
            opacity: 1;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-button-solid:hover:before {
            width: 100%;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-picture {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
            display: block;
            /* width divided by height */
            aspect-ratio: 0.78095238;
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-picture img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
    }
    /* Tablet - 768px */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
        #sbs-97 .cs-container {
            max-width: 80rem;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            /* 60px - 108px */
            gap: clamp(3.75rem, 7.8vw, 6.75rem);
        }
        #sbs-97 .cs-picture {
            /* 284px - 522px */
            width: clamp(17.75rem, 39.3vw, 32.625rem);
            /* 492px - 740px */
            height: clamp(30.75rem, 60.9vw, 46.25rem);
            /* prevents flexbox from squishing it */
            flex: none;
        }
    }
    /* Dark Mode */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-picture:before,
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-picture:after {
            background: var(--accent);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-topper {
            color: var(--primaryLight);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-text,
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-li,
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-title {
            color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-text {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-number {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            background-color: var(--primaryLight);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-button-solid {
            background-color: var(--primaryLight);
            color: #000;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbs-97 .cs-button-solid:hover {
            color: #fafbfc;
        }
    }

    /*-- -------------------------- -->
<---   Side By Side Reverse 2   -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

    /* Mobile - 360px */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
        #sbsr-2202 {
            padding: var(--sectionPadding);
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-container {
            width: 100%;
            /* changes to 1280px at tablet */
            max-width: 44rem;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            /* 48px - 64px */
            gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-content {
            /* set text align to left if content needs to be left aligned */
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 36.625rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            /* centers content horizontally, set to flex-start to left align */
            align-items: center;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-title {
            max-width: 30ch;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-text {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-weekdays,
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-weekends {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.6px;
            color: var(--bodyTextColor);
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-weekdays {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-button-solid {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            /* 46px - 56px */
            line-height: clamp(2.875rem, 5.5vw, 3.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            min-width: 9.375rem;
            margin: 2rem 0 0 0;
            /* prevents padding from adding to the width */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-button-solid:before {
            content: "";
            width: 0%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #000;
            opacity: 1;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-button-solid:hover:before {
            width: 100%;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-image-group {
            /* scales the whole section down and ties the font size to the vw and stops at 75% of the vale of 1em, changes at desktop */
            font-size: min(2.3vw, 0.75rem);
            /* everything inside this box is in ems so we can scale it all down proportionally with a font size */
            width: 39.375em;
            height: 39.1875em;
            order: -1;
            position: relative;
            /* prevents flexbox from squishing it */
            flex: none;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture {
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 8px solid #fff;
            display: block;
            position: absolute;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture1 {
            width: 24em;
            height: 29.375em;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture2 {
            width: 21.5625em;
            height: 31.875em;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-flower {
            /* 137px - 309px */
            width: clamp(8.5625rem, 20vw, 19.3125rem);
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            position: absolute;
            right: -2rem;
            bottom: -0.5rem;
        }
    }
    /* Tablet - 768px */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-container {
            max-width: 80rem;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-flower {
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    }
    /* Desktop - 1024px */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 64rem) {
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-container {
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: stretch;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-content {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            align-self: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-image-group {
            font-size: min(1.3vw, 1rem);
            height: auto;
            min-height: 39.1875em;
            order: 2;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture1 {
            height: 74.960128%;
        }
        #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture2 {
            height: 81.339719%;
        }
    }
    /* Dark Mode */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-title,
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-text,
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-weekdays,
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-weekends {
            color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite);
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-text {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        body.dark-mode #sbsr-2202 .cs-picture {
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }
    }
</style>
